    "They can efficiently handle diverse text-related tasks, saving significant human effort and time.",
    "We argue LLMs are best suited for qualitative research when they are working on the classification of specific texts.",
    "LLMs excel in text-related tasks, such as answering questions, summarizing information, or even engaging in conversation.",
